00:10:15.856 --> 00:10:16.296 A:middle
example.

00:10:16.776 --> 00:10:18.736 A:middle
We want to create an event

00:10:18.736 --> 00:10:20.546 A:middle
trigger which executes when the

00:10:20.546 --> 00:10:21.886 A:middle
