Event.

00:10:58.476 --> 00:10:59.486 A:middle
And we specify our target

00:10:59.486 --> 00:11:00.216 A:middle
characteristic.

00:10:59.486 --> 00:11:00.216 A:middle
characteristic.

00:11:01.066 --> 00:11:02.276 A:middle
In this case, it is a

