00:36:57.786 --> 00:36:58.896 A:middle
accessories are tested

00:36:59.016 --> 00:37:01.256 A:middle
thoroughly by MFi licenses and

00:36:59.016 --> 00:37:01.256 A:middle
thoroughly by MFi licenses and

00:37:01.256 --> 00:37:02.276 A:middle
audited by Apple.

00:37:03.806 --> 00:37:05.676 A:middle
