00:38:02.606 --> 00:38:04.246 A:middle
test your accessory and continue

00:38:04.246 --> 00:38:05.966 A:middle
to automate more and more test

00:38:05.966 --> 00:38:08.256 A:middle
cases, and we urge all MFi

